      • setLocation

        public void setLocation(com.spartanlaboratories.measurements.Location location)
        Sets where on the map this camera is located. The parameter will be the new absolute location of the camera, if the new location needs to be relative to the current location of the camera then use move(Location) instead.
        Parameters:
        location - the location on the map at which this camera is to be placed.

      • move

        public void move(Location locChange)
        "Moves" the camera by the coordinates in the given location. Similar to #setWorldLocation(Location) except instead of setting the absolute location of the camera this method changes the current location by the amount given in the parameter.
        Parameters:
        locChange - the amount by which the location of this camera changes.
